How To

!!!MAKE BACKUPS OF ALL MOVED OVERWRITTEN FILES OR ELSE!!!

Copy files/folders in etc to /etc
Build poweroff program ( See poweroff.cpp file )
Copy poweroff executable to /etc/StartupServices/poweroff
Copy runservices to /etc/StartupServices/runservices
Link /sbin/init to /etc/StartupServices/runservices
Link /sbin/shutdown and /sbin/reboot to /etc/StartupServices/runservices

